###############################################################################
# NOTES:
# - Start the server first: Rscript server.R
# - The server runs on http://localhost:8000
# - Prediction endpoints require a trained model in final_model/ directory
# - Run training first if model doesn't exist: GET /train
# - CSV file must contain all 31 feature columns (no Result column needed)
# - JSON predictions return: 0 = phishing, 1 = legitimate
# - Feature inputs should match the raw dataset (-1 = False/Not Present, 1 = True/Present, etc.)
# - Generate test data parameters:
#   * type: "phishing" (suspicious), "legitimate" (safe), or "random" (default)
#   * count: number of records (1-100, default: 1)
###############################################################################
